4	//! graph payload — the graphviz DOT text served at
5	//! `/thy/trace/N/interactive-graph-def/proof/…`.
6	//!
7	//! Everything here was derived from BLACK-BOX observation of captured payloads
8	//! and live probing of the compiled server; see `workspace/BEHAVIOR.md` for the
9	//! observed spec and `workspace/QUERIES.log` for the oracle interactions. No
10	//! tamarin-prover source was consulted.
11	//!
12	//! ## What it does
13	//! * [`model`] — an independent graph data model (nodes, edges, clusters, legend).
14	//! * [`dot::to_dot`] — a **byte-exact** DOT serializer for that model.
15	//! * [`term`] — a small term model backing abbreviation expansions.
16	//! * [`abbrev`] — node abbreviation: prefix derivation, per-prefix numbering,
17	//!   and byte-exact legend-table HTML.
